 Rapper Quavo and Girlfriend Saweetie American Rapper Quavo has stunned his girlfriend singer Saweetie as he gifted her a custom ‘icy’ Bentley for Christmas. The couple had gone for a trip on a private jet and they had just touched down when the exotic gift was presented to her. In the videos, Saweetie was extremely shocked but she got over her shock and checked out her new whip. The Bentley was adorned with ice with diamonds cut into the shape of a  ‘snowflake’.. 